Author: Timothy Willard [aut, cre], Justin Lessler [aut], ACCIDDA [cph, fnd]
Maintainer: Timothy Willard <twillard@unc.edu>
Description: Bayesian models for severity estimation analysis with the ability
  to perform analysis by strata as well as incorporating information obtained
  through active and passive surveillance. Work based on
  <doi:10.1093/aje/kwv452>.
